        "Limit afternoon naps"
      ],
      "feeling-tired": [
        "Evaluate your sleep environment",
        "Consider talking to a healthcare provider",
        "Track your sleep patterns",
        "Ensure you're getting enough physical activity"
      ]
    };

    const schedule = [
